interpretation: The Dominica flag is a symbol of the country's resilience and determination to overcome adversity. As a tarot card, it represents the power of nature and the ability to weather any storm. The lush greenery and blue waters depicted in the flag are a reminder of the beauty and abundance of the Caribbean. This card may suggest a need to connect with nature or tap into your own inner strength in the face of challenges. It can also represent a sense of pride in one's heritage and culture. Overall, the Dominica flag card encourages you to stay strong and persevere, knowing that you have the power to overcome any obstacle.
